/* RV32I tests using Python-assembled programs from rv32i_asm.py.
 * Tests are compiled from .s files via rv32i_asm.py, which outputs
 * uint32_t arrays embedded as C header.  This file includes them
 * and runs each program through the qsim RV32I simulation.
 */
